A multi-faceted role that encompassed many responsibilities, including:
• Community building and management; 
• events planning; 
• business development & strategic partnerships; 
• communications & marketing strategy; 
• content creation; 
• social media marketing;
• (plus some design work, sales, pitching). 

Achievements:
• Organized over 50 events for the Party with a Local community in multiple cities (including Ams, NYC & Sao Paulo)
• Played an instrumental role in the growth and development of the community (+100% growth) - and company as a whole.
• Oct ’16 to Feb ’17 - in NYC for the Techstars Connection accelerator. An incredible experience during which I learned a lot, met incredible people, and gained a full appreciation for start up co-working.
• Interviewed live by CMX on Community Management - watch it here: https://www.facebook.com/cmxnyc/videos/1662486884042948/?pnref=story
• Developed strategic partnerships with big brands including Budweiser & Time Out
